Oil prices are suppressed for many reasons, one of the main reasons is to keep the economy from crashing. US is prepared to raise the debt ceiling to 19,600,000,000,000. IMF warns Saudi Arabia will be broke by 2020. IMF has not admitted that the Chinese yuan will become a reserve currency and be included in the SDR basket of currencies. Russia will go up against OPEC. Obamacare exchanges and website does not check to see if people have valid Id’s, they are letting anyone signup
